Rare, well cared for 2, 065 SF, 3 bed 2.5 bath townhome w/tons of natural light. New 40k kitchen remodel with custom cabinets, quartz countertops & SS appliances. Primary bedroom ensuite with double vanity & walk-in closet. Large front porch and back deck in a peaceful, quiet, treed setting. Outdoor firepit area w/space for entertaining. Large shed for storage. Spacious garage w/workbench & extra storage. Recently remodeled laundry room and 4+ parking spaces. Highly desirable neighborhood near the heart of Fairhaven's historic district and its charming pubs, restaurants, bookstores and gift shops. 5 minute walk to the Ferry Terminal, Amtrak Station, Community Boating Center, and Marine Park. Steps away from the Interurban Trail too!

Step into your new sanctuary - a contemporary 2-bedroom, 1-bathroom manufactured home that embodies modern living. Nestled in a serene park setting, this property harmonizes comfort and style, creating an airy, welcoming ambiance from the moment you walk through the door. The spacious, well-lit living area seamlessly flows into the open kitchen, where stainless steel appliances, including a refrigerator, stove, dishwasher, and microwave, elevate both form and function. With its sleek design and abundant natural light, this kitchen is not just a culinary space but a statement of refined living. Additionally, the utility room offers convenient access to the back area through a rear door. Welcome to your new haven.

Incredible opportunity to be centrally located in Bellingham w/option to run your own business from your home. Across the street from the Rose Garden, & walking distance to Cornwall Park. Meticulously maintained home that has been well cared for. Immerse yourself w/charm when walking into this 1930s craftsman. Beautiful hardwood floors, wood trim, doors, & shutters. Large living & dining room off the entry w/recently updated kitchen that includes quartz countertops & SS appliances. Downstairs daylight basement is permitted to run your own business out of, or convert it & have MIL/separate unit. Dont miss out on the number of possibilities this home has to offer. Close access to the hospital, grocery stores & more.

Detailed craftsmanship throughout this 4bed, 3ba on a fenced one-of-a-kind lot with breathtaking mountain views. House features, sparkling kitchen complete with soft close cabinetry, quartz counter-tops & tiled backsplash. Primary bedroom with walk-in closet and private bath. High efficiency heating & A/C. Nice covered outdoor living area, allows quality outdoor living in the PNW. Enjoy a morning coffee on your patio listening to the birds. Property back to a greenbelt; great for added privacy & relaxation. Only 35 min from Bellingham, 45 min from renowned Mt. Baker ski resort, 15 min to Canadian border. Minutes to fishing, swimming, hiking & more. A truly one of a kind home with breathtaking mountain views.

This adorable seaside getaway with low bank waterfront and spectacular southwest views is the perfect place to unwind, reconnect with nature, and create memories that will last a lifetime. This close-knit neighborhood, only 20 minutes to downtown Bellingham, is a hidden gem in Whatcom County. It would make an excellent vacation home, short-term rental or primary residence. Well-maintained manufactured home provides an open floor plan, sunlit living area, and a private deck for soaking up the sun and the sea breeze. With easy and direct access to the beach, hop onto your kayak or paddle board and explore the bay right from your front yard! Come and enjoy the best of what the Pacific NW has to offer.
nearby_schools: Lummi Elementary School, Lummi High School, Ferndale School District

text: Sitting on an open lot, this Ideal travel trailer has been lovingly maintained and makes for a perfect introductory property to The Glen. Inside, you have everything you need for a comfortable home away from home, including an add-a-room, perfect for shaping into whatever kind of flex space you need. Outside, a shed sits on the property for additional or larger storage items. Or sit around the campfire and enjoy the nature around you. The Glen is zoned recreational for 120 days of use out of the year and has all the amenities you could want, including 2 pools, hot tub, tennis court, library, laundry mat, 2 clubhouse, 24 hr security, gated entry, & play areas.

South Hill living at its best! Boasting 1, 832 Square Feet with endless Ocean views from the Primary Bedroom, living room, dining room and kitchen. Primary suite includes a tub and cedar Sauna. Two additional bedrooms with a second bath adjoining in the hallway along with full size washer and dryer off the kitchen. There are 2 covered parking spaces assigned to the unit with a storage closet. Let's talk about location - it can't be beat!! You are close to Old Town Fairhaven, the Bellingham Farmers Market, numerous coffee shops and restaurants to name a few of the amenities this location affords. Bellingham is known for its water views, hiking, biking and all of this is within a short walk or drive from your Cliffhouse Condo!

This fully fenced lot boasts a view of greenspace, helping make it feel like a private home away from home. Enjoy sitting around the campfire or on the large covered deck and enjoy the nature surrounding you. Inside the lovingly maintained Jayco trailer, there are plenty of places to sleep between the bedroom and two sets of bunkbeds. Spread out and relax in your own private get away! The Glen is zoned recreational for 120 days of use out of the year and has all the amenities you could want, including 2 pools, hot tub, tennis court, library, laundry mat, 2 clubhouse, 24 hr security, gated entry, & play areas.

Experience epic fun at Grand Bay condos beach! Vibrant seaside-style resort life w/in golf cart zone life with Birch Bay restaurants, Beach Cat Brewery, library, parks. Full time or second home. 2nd floor condo w/elevator outside entry w/south-facing balcony & partial water view. Fully turnkey. Stylish finishes, radiant floor heat in baths. 1, 023 SF, 2 BR, 2 full BA. Built 2010. On site amenities- community hot tub, storage for kayaks, paddleboards & bikes. Association owns grass field by mouth of Terrell Creek & beach rights, firepits in front. 2 pets OK. Dues inc. maintenance, insurance, garbage. Beach berm in front w/ 1.5 mile of level surface. Small boats can anchor in front Aug-Oct crabbing season. Week minimum rentals OK. Sunsets!

Calm. Cool. Collected. The Cypress uses intentional design and refined styling to present a setting evoking a gentler side of living - one crafted to keep stress at bay. Soften your mood as you approach the artful columns punctuating the contemporary facade. Through its custom-designed wood and frosted glass panel entry door, let the semi-enclosed, with option to fully enclose, Home Office model your life. Need an extra live-in space? Modify the Home Office into a Guest Suite with Bath or Guest Room to provide that perfect live-in option. Upstairs, two of three Secondary Bedrooms offer ample Walk-In Closets. The third is spacious enough for two twin beds - and right around the corner from the Grand Suite, creating an ideal arrangement for soothing sleepless children. A baby nursery, perhaps? When paired with the oversized Dressing Room and Grand Bathroom, meanwhile, the luxurious Grand Suite is all about the essence of adult-time "aaaah." Like a gift to yourself, close each day by stepping across the large, porcelain tile flooring into the sophisticated frameless walk-in shower or ease effortless into the warmth of the designer free-standing soaking tub. Across from the upstairs Leisure Room, serene hours begin again each morning after descending the Great Room-access staircase.

Extraordinary 5-bedroom traditional country home, entirely remodeled Spring 2024, between Bellingham and Lynden. 2 levels, with utilities divided; extra kitchen and separate level living option. Surrounded by a large chunk of land and a brand-new Thrive luxury home community, enjoy the established garage, BBQ area, plenty of space available for additional shops/greenhouses, etc. Perfect property for those seeking a clear palette for all their landscaping dreams & colors. Situated across from golf course, 6918 RR is a fun classic, with that brand new feeling! Romantically designed reno, with contemporary touches throughout. Heat pump warms/cools you, year-round. No HOA; no dues; no demands. Classy kitchen; deck/patio. Flows well; lives well.

Incredibly rare inland pacific waterfront at Calluna Estates. Nearly 200' of waterfront estate dream property. Expansive stretch from the San Juan Islands to the Canadian Gulf Islands. The view will knock your socks off. Imagine your incredible waterfront estate or private compound where you enjoy boating, fishing, swimming & beach combing out your back door. Private level treed setting. Just minutes to Vancouver B.C., fine dining, shopping, golf, & marina and 1/4 mil from Point Whitehorn Marine Reserve features 54 acres of forest, bluff and beach, with an ADA accessible trail to spectacular viewpoints of the Strait of Georgia and San Juan Islands. A switchback path descends from the bluff to access the windswept beach below.

Single story home in cul-de-sac, wonderfully updated in 2020, with new stove, fridge, and flooring. And an even newer water heater. Primary bedroom has dual closets and full on-suite bathroom. Home was built to be energy efficient and also boasts a laundry room with brand new washer and dryer. Outside you'll find an over-sized carport and attached storage area. A new fence fully encloses the backyard and partially fenced in the front. Clean and move-in ready, for owner to occupy or would make a fantastic rental.

Great opportunity in Sudden Valley! Surrounded by trees on a quiet street, this 1700+ square foot home has endless possibilities. Kitchen, living room and dining room flow together with an open concept layout. Light and bright with lots of windows and direct access to your spacious wrap around deck. 2 bedrooms on the main floor and a fully finished basement with 2 bedrooms, a den and a separate entrance. Could be used as a MIL suite or a short term/long term rental. Enjoy the Sudden Valley community including boat launch, golf course, community pool, tennis courts, parks, endless trails, boat launch and beach access on Lake Whatcom!

Experience breathtaking sunset vistas over Birch Bay from the exquisite Terrell Creek Landing condominiums! Securely nestled within a well-appointed building, this top-floor unit boasts convenient elevator access directly from the lobby. Step inside to discover an inviting open layout, highlighted by a gourmet kitchen adorned with granite countertops, a gas range, and stainless steel fridge. The kitchen effortlessly flows into a breakfast bar and a separate dining area, perfect for entertaining guests. Unwind in the cozy living room, complete with a gas fireplace, before stepping out onto the covered deck to savor the panoramic view. With two bedrooms and two full bathrooms, this residence offers both comfort and convenience. Just a leisure

Stunning 2020 destination trailer located on a quiet cul-de-sac in Div 3 of the Glen at Maple Falls. You'll be wowed when you step inside! Theatre seating, solid surface counters w/ pendant lights, stainless steel sink & appliances & wood blinds are just some of the touches you'll discover. The bedroom features W/D hookups, there's central vac & a spacious loft upstairs for even more sleeping space. Outside there's a paver patio where you can spread out & soak up the sun in this bright, spacious lot just steps from the Gorge Trail which leads to the Nooksack River. Community amenities include two pools, parks, playgrounds, disc golf, tennis, Nooksack River access, 24/7 security & more. Limited to 120 days/year occupancy. No rentals.

Here's that ready to go lot in beautiful Semiahmoo. Located in the desirable Royal Troon development, this picturesque lot has water, sewer, and power too. Gorgeous landscaping framed by huge cedars. Over 1/3 acre too! You could be building by summer!

Welcome to River-Walk, a unique NW Washington community offering attractive design, luxurious finishes & pedestrian-friendly connectivity to Lynden. Residents can walk or bike a few blocks to downtown Lyndens quaint restaurants and stores, located less than two hours to Seattle, Vancouver, B.C., Mt. Baker and the San Juan Islands. Lot 33 is on River-Walk West, reserved for 55 & older. It offers a comfortable 1765 sq. ft. with 2 bedrooms, 1.75 bathrooms + office or flex space & many upgrades. The home faces south w/ beautiful views of Mt. Baker! The gourmet kitchen is highlighted by quartz countertops & islands with full waterfall drops.

Rare Waterfront Estate size parcel. 10+ acres of Incomparable Southern exposure with nearly 300' of high bank waterfront. Minutes to I-5 & U.S./Canada Border. Eagles, Great Blue Herons & other wildlife abound. Design & build your dream home here and enjoy privacy and serenity of the best the Pacific Northwest has to offer. Escape to this quiet community from the hectic area you currently call home! Just 1/4 mile to Point Whitehorn Marine Reserve features 54 acres of forest, bluff and beach, with an ADA accessible trail to spectacular viewpoints of the Strait of Georgia and San Juan Islands. A switchback path descends from the bluff to access the windswept beach below.

This setup can't be beat! The cozy trailer with add-a-room is set far back on the lot, giving you plenty of outdoor space. Whether you want to add a shed and/or gazebo, or maybe host more guests in a visiting RV, there's room. Inside sleeps 8 guests between the bedroom, bunk room and the addition which has a futon bunk bed. Bring everyone! There's a covered deck for dreary days and a paver patio around the fire pit for songs, stories and s'mores. A dine in kitchen and full bathroom, too. It's got everything you need to start making memories. Community amenities include two pools, parks, playgrounds, disc golf, tennis, Nooksack River access, 24/7 security and more. Limited to 120 days/year occupancy. No rentals.

Introducing this meticulously renovated 4-bed, 2-bath retreat nestled in the desirable Blaine area, just a short walk to the water. This charming home on over 1/4 of an acre features a detached shop. Its recent top-to-bottom transformation includes a new roof, all-new plumbing, new electrical, a new on-demand hot water tank, and nearly all-new windows, in addition to new flooring, cabinets, appliances, and countertops. Enjoy the modern kitchen, cozy living area, and main-level primary bedroom for ultimate convenience. With a fully fenced yard and AC heat pumps, this home offers year-round comfort. Don't miss out on this perfect blend of style and functionality!

Welcome to 'The Lake House, ' where every detail embodies the essence of luxury living. Tucked away from the road, a long driveway opens to a lawn with fruit trees and a pickleball court. This exquisite estate sits on 1.25 acres of beautifully landscaped ground with perfect sun exposure and 109 feet of lake frontage. Step into a world of true indoor-outdoor living where windows vanish into walls & the indoors flow out across the expansive lawn to the lake & dock. For those seeking the ultimate waterfront lifestyle, look no further. Every aspect of this home has been thoughtfully curated to provide the perfect blend of luxury & comfort. Sit back, relax, and immerse yourself in the beauty... after your morning glassy surf session, of course ;)

Priced to sell! Great lot in Gate 13, ULID has been paid on lot 55. A lovely and private lot to build your next home, this could be the one!. All Sudden valley amenities include golf course, marina, hiking trails, swimming pool, tennis courts, beaches, boat launch and 24/7 security.

RARE DOUBLE LOT adjacent to each other, This home packs so much into 394 sq feet and comes mostly furnished. With walking distance to the cabana and outdoor pool. Walk onto the the large deck with large sitting area. The living room and kitchen are well equipped to make watching tv relaxing and fixing your favorite meal. White fridge and beautiful hood. 2 Large garden shed. Propane furnace, electric fireplace. You do not want to miss out on this fantastic home, located in a back corner with some privacy. Fridge is about 1 yr old.

It is not often that one finds a home that is in better than new condition...but this single level home definitely is! It is located on a corner parcel that is just steps from the world renown Galbraith Trail system, Whatcom Falls Park and the best donut shop in town! This single level home has been lightly lived in and has an open floor plan with a privately situated primary suite and all the living areas are spacious as well as the bedrooms. There's a covered deck that looks out to the fully fenced rear yard and the forested ravine beyond (this property extends beyond the fence and down into the ravine). The quality finishes and architectural details make this home outstanding and this community and the location are highly sought after.

Experience the joy of everyday living in this stunning retreat on 95' of Lake Whatcom waterfront. Step inside and you'll be swept away by the serene atmosphere & dramatic lake views. Entertaining is effortless with the great room opening to an expansive covered deck. Chef kitchen with abundant counters makes food prep a breeze. Primary suite with spa bath, fire place, deck & BIG views. Spend your mornings sipping coffee on the deck while taking in sunrise. After an active day on the lake, unwind in the hot-tub and BBQ on 1 of 2 covered decks. Opportunity abounds with lower-level rec room and 2 bed apartment plus, a bonus 1 bed apartment above the oversized 3-car garage. Lush lawn, beach, dock and boat lift. A home for an amazing lifestyle.

Knotty-pine interior walls, throughout this sweet cabin, full of historic charm, and cute wrap around front porch. What more could you ask? Built 1896, on a huge (.47 acre) 'double' lot. Park-like surroundings, cultivated over 20 years by a green-thumb gardener and sculptor. New roof in 2017. Just needs your personal touch to update and make it shine again. Easy access to the restaurants and services of the friendly community of Nooksack/Everson

Generously sized 1/4 Acre level building lot on low traffic street backing onto larger properties. Recent soils test confirms lot is suitable for an on-site septic system; water and electricity are at the street.

ENJOY ISLAND LIVING WITHOUT THE FERRY! Experience spectacular sun filled southerly views of the San Juan and Gulf Islands, Strait of Georgia, and the Olympic Mountains. An iconic mid-century modern architectural statement situated on a beachfront 3/4 acre, and on a quiet non through lane. A classic original one level, but tastefully updated inside and out including a large deck and patio for dining alfresco. An extremely private and quiet location for memorable campfires and walks on the beach, while you watch whales, seals, eagles, and boats of all sizes pass by. Only minutes from Semiahmoo Resort which offers excellent dining, world class golf, and a large marina with slips available to purchase. Truly one of a kind and a legacy property!

Experience effortless living in this fantastic low-maintenance single-level home. Situated in the serene Silver Beach neighborhood, tucked away on a tranquil cul-de-sac just minutes from shopping, schools, Lake Whatcom, parks and trails. This gem rests on a generous private .29 acre lot adorned with a garden shed and mature landscaping, bordering city-owned greenspace alive with songbirds. Meticulously maintained, featuring hardi-plank siding, energy-efficient HVAC. Wired for security and a generator for peace of mind. Trex decking invites outdoor relaxation. Inside is a fantastic floorplan, custom Hunter Douglas window coverings, renovated baths, a sunny office and spacious kitchen. Welcome to a lifestyle where every day feels effortless.

Classic Northwest one-level living on private 8.46 acre lot. 3 bed/2 ba with over 2K square feet will make you feel instantly home. Chefs will love the XL kitchen with tons of cabinets and prep space, second sink, eating bar and adjacent breakfast nook. Comfortable blend of formal and informal spaces with soaring ceilings, large deck and patio to extend your entertaining (and living) space out doors. Primary w/firepalce, ensure bath with dual sinks, soaking tub and shower. French doors in primary open to large deck and beautiful territorial views. Oversized, energy efficient windows throughout for tons of light! Propane and Electric options for heating, cooling and appliances. Huge 780SF 3 car garage- room for your toys and projects.

Gently sloping lot with views of Boundary Bay and North Shore Mountains from a second story home. Almost 1/4 Acre with 80' frontage. This is truly a great opportunity to build your dream home or your vacation cottage. Maple Beach is just a short bike ride away.

BRING A BOAT! A tiny cottage designed for a huge lifestyle at a vacation community on Lake Whatcom. This popular floor design (Townsend) has a spacious sleeping loft, and a stunning rooftop deck with a fireplace. Entertain loved ones and BBQ on the covered side deck. Store lake toys in the shed and enjoy the short stroll to the beach. Includes a mooring Buoy, that's a big deal! Secure your lake access, explore the park-like 14-acre property with resort amenities and fun activities - then retreat & relax in your perfect getaway cottage on the lake!

Welcome to this exquisite 2022 park model! Upgraded features include 4-season insulation package, enhanced R-rating floors and roof, trex decking and a 30-gallon hot water heater. Revel in the interior's elegance with full-sized stainless steel appliances, a charming farmhouse sink, and a large loft for additional sleeping space. The bathroom presents a luxurious tile shower and ample storage space. The oversized bedroom accommodates a King size bed. Outside is a shed and a TV in weather proof cabinet. Situated in The Glen, enjoy recreational zoning allowing for 120 days of annual use and many amenities such as 2 pools, a hot tub, tennis court, library, laundry facilities, 2 clubhouses, 24-hour security, gated entry, and play areas.

This 3 Bedroom, 2 Bath home with a 380 Sq. Ft. insulated garage is situated at the end of a quiet cul-de-sac. Enjoy tiled bathrooms and wood laminate flooring in the kitchen and living room. Carpets in bedrooms were recently cleaned and fence installed. Front porch is covered. Large driveway for extra parking when entertaining. This house is a must see!

Welcome to Lakeway Mobile Estates, a welcoming 55+ community offering convenience and comfort. This charming home boasts a brand new roof for lasting durability, complemented by fresh new carpeting throughout, enhancing both style and coziness. Enjoy the ease of access to nearby shops and a convenient bus stop, with a handy shed for storage and a fenced yard perfect for pets to roam freely. Relax on the spacious carport and porch, both with newer roofs for added protection. Stay cozy year-round with the efficiency of a new ductless mini-split heater and a recently installed hot water tank, ensuring comfort and affordability. Discover the perfect blend of modern amenities and a desirable location at Lakeway Mobile Estates.

Creekside, high and dry, in an excellent location- Beautiful Character Home! An enclosed, large Gazebo Room w/ a large hot-tub, tall shop building all on an 11, 326 sf lot. 3 bedroom 2 bath in great condition. Cozy country decor upgraded 2021- all new paint and flooring. Main floor: Kitchen is bright and spacious with lovely dinette eating area. Living/dining is large and comfortable, w/ lots of windows, a primary bedroom, plus, bath & utility. Upper floor: 2 bedrooms w/ another full bath, plus a small room office, den or playroom. Lots of parking. Detached shop, wood burning stove & loft for more storage. Home is wired for a Gentran system. Sandy creek-side area w/ firepit. Watch the salmon, relax & rest, in the peace of your own backyard.

Offered for the first time, this Maple Beach seaside cottage is not to be missed. This property features 2 beds, 1 bath, and a large loft with stunning ocean views. Bring your vision and your tool belt to maximize the property's potential. Charming heritage details throughout and an expansive layout with a large kitchen and original brick wood fireplace in the heart of the living room. Stunning panoramic bay, city, and mountain views from the covered front porch and back deck. Across the road is the premier beach of the Point, with sandbars for days, and warm bath water in the Summer. Newer septic system, and lots of garden space and storage in the walkout basement. One-of-a-kind offering to experience the Point Roberts lifestyle.

Welcome to 206 E Wiser Lake Rd! With views of Wiser lake and the Mountains this 1/2 acre lot is the perfect place to build your dream home and have plenty of room for a shop or outbuildings. Great sandy soil and no wetlands makes for a simple septic and basement options, water share included! Fantastic location on Wiser Lake Rd just East of the Guide Meridian means you're 5 mins from Lynden and 10 mins from Bellingham! Amazing opportunity for one of the few remaining lots in this area.

Nestled within the serene expanse of the pnw forest on a 4.57-acre property, minutes from town, this newly constructed modern home boasts an impressive 3090 sqft of contemporary living space. Expansive windows throughout the home frame picturesque views of the lush forest. The open-concept living area features vaulted ceilings, white oak engineered h/wd floors, and a stunning double sided fireplace. Gourmet kitchen, where top of the line appliances, waterfall edge island, and a large walk in pantry create an ideal environment for culinary creativity. Two laundry rooms provide added convenience. 3 bedrooms and an extra finished room/nursery/gym upstairs. Buy with confidence!

Fantastic opportunity to build your lake home on Reed Lake. The lot is lightly treed with access to the lake for water activities all year around. Installed septic conveniently connected to an off sight drain field allowing maximum overall building area. Active Glenhaven community with well maintained amenities. Clubhouse, seasonal swimming pool, tennis, trails, playgrounds and more.

NEW PRICE! This lovely one owner, one-level home is nestled in the Geneva hillside above Lake Whatcom. A spacious living room has a cozy gas fireplace and lots of natural light, with a peak-a-boo view of Lake Whatcom. The eat-in kitchen opens onto a multipurpose/dining room, plus a sunroom to enjoy in all seasons. The primary bedroom is truly a master suite, with space for a king-size bed and a sitting area. A triple garage provides room for vehicles, storage AND a work area. NEW in 2023: high efficiency furnace, air conditioning and refrigerator. Located blocks from the lake and on a non-through quiet street. Fully fenced. This home is designed for comfort!

Attention developers and builders, 7 great lots for sale in an established neighborhood as an assemblage. With 7 potential building sites together, the logistics of building just got easy! Property has trees and brush; the lots have not been cleared or grubbed. Water, sewer, and power are in the street. The lots are located in the desirable Birch Bay area near fast growing Blaine, which makes this a great location! No permits have been applied for, and no studies have been done. Call your consultants and get started on your next project now! APNs: 4051240254000000, 4051240253930000, 4051240253860000, 4051240253790000; 4051240403850000, 4051240393920000, 4051240394000000.

Escape to your own piece of paradise nestled in the foothills of majestic Mt. Baker! This vacation lot offers the ultimate getaway, featuring a 2006 Dutchman camper, complete with an additional bunkhouse for extra guests. Embrace outdoor living with both an outdoor kitchen and interior kitchen, perfect for entertaining under the open skies. Situated on a lush level lot, this property boasts numerous amenities within a gated community, including a year-round indoor heated pool, parks, and trails for endless adventure. Whether you're into fishing, hiking, or skiing, this location has it all. Don't miss your chance to own a slice of heaven in this sought-after destination!

50' slip on E dock! 1 of only 2 slips with 50 amp service -- rare find! Great facilities and home to one of the best managed Marin's in the Pacific Northwest! Key-less entry, full service laundry and shower building. Picnic area with outdoor games, BBQ, seating areas. Wonderful marina store with caf and local artwork displays...short walk to the Inn at Semiahmoo with restaurants, spa and pool amenities. Marina has Wi-Fi, active yacht club, and resurfaced dock. Great place to moor your boat!

Classic 1966 rambler on a large fenced lot perfectly located deep on quiet cul-de-sac near the top of one of Bellingham's most sought after neighborhoods. This Toledo hill beauty is 2790 sf , 4 bd. 3 baths on 14, 824 sf lot with fully fenced back yard. This is a home entertainers gold mine. 1/2 the back yard is inground pool w/hot tub surrounded by huge patio w/ fireplace bbq area all fenced in for safety and the other half is wide open for your playground / garden / lawn / imagination. All this is totally private and screened by landscaping and fence. You'll always be excited to get home to this private oasis in the heart of fantastic Bellingham. Literally minutes from everywhere you want to be and easy access to major thru roads and I-5.

Welcome to 202 E Wiser Lake Rd! This 1/2 acre lot is the perfect place to build your dream home and have plenty of room for a shop or outbuildings. Great sandy soil and no wetlands makes for a simple septic and basement options, water share included! Fantastic location on Wiser Lake Rd just East of the Guide Meridian means you're 5 mins from Lynden and 15 mins from Bellingham! Amazing opportunity for one of the few remaining lots in this area.

This move in ready, craftsman style home is still in like-new condition. The interior features an open concept living area with high ceiling, a kitchen that boasts a large island + seating for 3, shaker style cabinets, quartz countertops, tile backsplash, black stainless appliances + don't miss the large walk-in pantry. Outside you will find ample yard space, a covered patio that steps down to an additional, larger patio & fully fenced back yard with big double gate on one side. There is also a huge gravel area beside the long concrete driveway perfect for parking an RV, extra vehicles & all your toys. It's a short trip to Baker! Make this your 1st home, your next home or a VRBO!

For the countless reasons a sweeping Grand Suite on the main level fits your specific needs, The Zinnia delivers an unparalleled arrangement. This top-of-its-class design is at its' best when revealing surprises that soar and expand with flawless details. Intuitively, the main floor, far corner-set Grand Suite is arranged beyond a privacy-maximizing vestibule opening into the sleeping quarters. It's the entree to the Grand Bathroom where thick Quartz shimmers on the broad dual-sink vanity under sleek designer lighting. Even without an excuse for a soothing soak, plunge into the decadent stand-alone tub or let the Grohe fixtures immerse you in the spray of the frameless glass shower. Store fluffy fresh towels in the on-trend cabinets or put extras in your generous Dressing Room. Upstairs, all three Secondary Bedrooms host their own Walk-In Closets. They also access an ingenious dual-entry Bathroom. The nearby Leisure Room fills an entire quadrant of this level and can be enclosed to enhance privacy or an extra Bedroom. For a double-pop of wow, the upstairs hallway opens to main-level Foyer at one end and to the magnificent Great Room at the other via half-wall staircase. Luxury living space here hums throughout. The gourmet Kitchen - an upscale synthesis of KitchenAid appliances and designer tile backsplash - is a modern fusion with the sophisticated Dining and Great Rooms.

Nestled along the scenic fairways of the golf course, this spacious 3700+ sq ft custom-built one owner home is now available for the first time. This generous 3-bedroom home hosts 2 ensuites, with additional living space and office upstairs. Enjoy the architectural marvels like vaulted ceilings and large windows that flood the home with natural light, serene views and wildlife. With its thoughtfully designed layout, this home provides the perfect canvas for your personal touches. Enjoy comfort and style in the vibrant community offering amenities - private beaches, seasonal pool, parks, gym, marina, & the 18-hole championship golf course.

Welcome to your new condo! Nestled within the picturesque surroundings of Sudden Valley Bellingham, this home boasts high ceilings, vaulted windows, and a sleek modern update. The layout features an open living space with heated floors, a brand-new kitchen, and a secluded loft bedroom upstairs with its own ensuite bath. Only a short walk to a plethora of amenities including the pool, restaurants, tennis court, trails, golf course, marina, library, and Lake Louise! But wait, there's more! This condo offers an enticing opportunity as a lucrative Airbnb, bringing in $130 per night with no rental cap. Whether you choose to make it your primary residence, a getaway, or a savvy investment property, the possibilities are endless.

Welcome to 534 Woodbury Way! Walk through your front door to an open living, dining room, and kitchen. Picture-perfect open-concept living spills onto a deck, with privacy and enough sun for your plants to thrive. The builders left no detail out when designing this luxury home. Walk-in pantry, gas fireplace, stainless steel appliances and luxury vinyl flooring are just a few of the spectacular finishes in this house.
